---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Hi, I'm Cass — a web designer who reviews SaaS tools for solopreneurs and creators.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Hi, I'm Cass 👋</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray prose-lg max-w-none prose-a:text-violet-600">
      <p>
        I'm a web designer who's spent years building websites and funnels for people selling online courses, digital products, and communities. In the process, I've tried an embarrassing number of tools.
      </p>
      <p>
        Some were genuinely great. Some were overhyped. A lot were just okay for the wrong reasons.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>This blog exists because I kept getting asked the same question:</strong> "What tool should I use for X?" So instead of answering the same DMs over and over, I'm writing it all down here.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every review is based on real use — not press releases, not feature lists, not sponsored posts. Just honest opinions from someone who's been in the weeds with these tools.
      </p>

      <h2>A note on affiliate links</h2>
      <p>
        Some links on this site are affiliate links, which means I earn a small commission if you sign up through them — at no extra cost to you. I only recommend tools I'd actually use or have genuinely liked. I'll always disclose when a link is affiliate.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a tool you want me to review? Questions about something I've covered? You can reach me at <a href="mailto:cass@saaswithcass.com">cass@saaswithcass.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
